org.elasticsearch.repositories.s3

Interface S3Repository.Repository

  • Enclosing class:
    S3Repository

    public static interface S3Repository.Repository
    Per S3 repository specific settings. Same settings as Repositories settings but without the repositories.s3 prefix. If undefined, they use the repositories.s3.xxx equivalent setting.
